## Slash Commands

Workflow follows the spec-driven development pipeline:

1. `specforge spec <feature>` — Generate feature specification (`spec.md`)
2. `specforge plan <feature>` — Generate implementation plan (`plan.md`)
3. `specforge tasks <feature>` — Generate task breakdown (`tasks.md`)
4. `specforge implement <feature>` — Execute implementation from tasks
5. `specforge check` — Run prerequisite checks

